    <summaries>
      <summary>
        <versionCode>00</versionCode>
        <actionDate>2007-11-06</actionDate>
        <actionDesc>Introduced in House</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2007-11-29T22:42:05Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Healthy Families and Dedicated Teachers Tax Relief Act of 2007 - Amends the Internal Revenue Code to: (1) extend through 2013 the tax credit for residential energy efficient property expenditures; (2) extend through 2012 the tax deductions for expenses of elementary and secondary school educators and qualified tuition and related expenses; (3) make permanent the tax deduction for state and local general sales taxes; and (4) make permanent the exemption from tax penalties for premature retirement plan distributions for charitable purposes.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
    <title>Healthy Families and Dedicated Teachers Tax Relief Act of 2007</title>
